    mem:content "Temporary `[DIAG][commit-t]` instrumentation used for the remote commit-t debugging pass has been removed after the fix landed. The detailed probes in `graph_commit_builder.rs`, `ledger_manager.rs`, `lib.rs::refresh`, `binary_range.rs`, and most of `peer/sync_task.rs` are gone. A single low-volume `tracing::debug!` remains in `peer/sync_task.rs` for successful SSE-triggered cache refresh completion (`\"refreshed cached ledger from SSE update\"`)." ;
